-- Critical real-time collision avoidance for autonomous drone fleets.
-- Formal verification: DO-178C DAL A | ED-269 | ISO 26262 ASIL D
-- 
-- V3 invariants: PSI_V3, PHI_CRITICAL, BETA, K_CYCLES
